<div class="sub-content-header">Official CES Hotels Now Accepting Reservations for 2010 Show</div>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i><span class="smallText">Jun 08, 2009 02:38:59</span></i>

<br /><br />

All official CES hotels are now accepting reservations for the 2010 International CES. The only thing more important than registering for CES is booking hotel&nbsp;accommodations for CES. Many properties sell out months in advance, so reserve yours right away. For the budget-minded,&nbsp;nine hotels currently are offering nightly rates under $150. Visit <A href="http://www.CESweb.org/hotel">www.CESweb.org/hotel</A> to book your room today.<BR><BR>Remember, the complimentary CES shuttles are only offered to/from official CES hotels. Save money, and&nbsp; leave your car at home! 
